![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c0c78bea-d0b5-4bab-bd57-cbedc91b132e/20240402_110417.jpg?format=original)

During an interview with Screengeek, Sam Raimi addressed rumors surrounding his involvement with Marvel’s “AVENGERS: SECRET WARS”:

“I love 90% of the Marvel heroes that I’ve read in the great Stan Lee Marvel Universe comic books. I would love to work with Marvel again. I hope they had a good experience with me. They haven’t asked me yet. I hope they do.”

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/395e2edc-d6dd-462d-b60f-1ce2f4acba36/20240402_110418.jpg?format=original)